DeAngelo Andre EVANS, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-1919 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 27, 2018 EMAS, LUCK and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of mandamus, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied as moot.
